WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
Alex walks through San Francisco's financial district.

00:03.500 --> 00:06.000
They study how light creates geometric patterns on buildings.

00:06.500 --> 00:09.000
"Cities are living art galleries," Alex observes.

00:09.500 --> 00:12.000
They sketch the interplay of shadows and reflections.

00:12.500 --> 00:15.000
The urban energy flows into their dynamic composition.